<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM2.6">
<l>muṟṟi lāta piḷḷaika ḷōmmulai pōntilā tōmai nāṭoṟum</l>
<l>ciṟṟiṉ mēliṭṭuk koṇṭu nīciṟi tuṇṭu tiṇṇeṉa nāmatu</l>
<l>kaṟṟi lōṅkaṭa laiya ṭaittarak karku laṅkaḷai muṟṟavuñ</l>
<l>ceṟṟilaṅ kaiyaip pūca lākkiya cēvakā vemmai vātiyēl.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There are a few [reasons for what] you [do] to us immature whose breasts are not full [yet],</l>
<l>using our little [sand] house [as a pretext] everyday.</l>
<l>We do not know [what] for sure.</l>
<l>O Warrior who turned Laṅkā into a battle[-field] after completely killing the Rākṣasa clan</l>
<l>[by] blocking the sea [with a bridge]! Do not distress us!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
